visual.name: RingChartByMAQSoftware
visual.description: A doughnut chart represent data as slices, where the size of each slice is determined by the slice value relative to the sum of the values of all slices. Each data series that you plot in a doughnut chart adds a ring to the chart. These rings have different colors for easy representation of the data slices in doughnut chart.

dataRoles.name: Category
dataRoles.description: The categorical field to show color

position.description: Select the position for the legend

showTitle.description: Display a title for legend symbols

detailedLegend.description: Displaying the legend details based on selection

labelPrecision.description: Select the number of decimal places to display
Select the number of decimal places to display

enumeration.value: Category, data value, percent of total

secondarySummaryLabels.description: Summary label options for Secondary measure

fill1.description: Font color for the donut title

fontSize.description: Font size for the donut title

backgroundColor.description: Background color for the donut title

tooltipText.description: Tooltip text for the donut title

PrimaryMeasure.description: Indicator based on sign for Primary measure. This is applicable only if 'Primary threshold' field is not selected

Threshold.description: Threshold value for Primary measure. This is applicable only if 'Primary threshold' field is not selected

Total_Threshold.description: Threshold value for Primary measure total. This is applicable only if 'Primary threshold' field is not selected

upArrow.description: Option to set color of up arrow

downArrow.description: Option to set color of down arrow

SecondaryMeasure.description: Indicator for secondary measure. This is applicable only if 'Secondary threshold' field is not selected

SMThreshold.description: Threshold value for secondary measure. This is applicable only if 'Secondary threshold' field is not selected

SMTotalThreshold.description: Threshold value for secondary measure total. This is applicable only if 'Secondary threshold' field is not selected

upArrow.description: Option to set color of up arrow

downArrow.description: Option to set color of down arrow

animation.description: Option to turn on or off the animation

nodatatext.description: Option to provide text message if there is no data
